title: Project First Strike Border Blueprints Bug
body:
I Bought the First Strike Augment + Bundle on the day of release before it was fixed where I didn't receive any of the bonus items. I look today and I now finally have the ward, and the 3 project icons. EM Caster, Hyper Edge and Decrypter. But I don't have any of the First strike loading border Blueprints in my hextech crafting inventory or the 3 cores you get when you buy the Ashe, Ekko and Katarina Cache's.

Here's the icons I already have: http://puu.sh/qoWqH/ede8be1a56.jpg

replies.body:
Hey there,

Has this been resolved yet?

You should probably [contact Player Support](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/requests/new) about this as they're the only ones who can help with account-specific issues.
same, but you lucky, i still dont have 3 icons
